</taxonomicName>
species by the presence of a velvet black median macula on the elytra and longer body size (
<quantity id="4CE91CD32278FFC4FD8B25AEFD34FF3C" box="[634,739,187,213]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.06" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" unit="mm" value="10.6">10.6 mm</quantity>
